entities

Class Street

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.Street

  • public class Street
extends java.lang.Object
    Street class represents one unique street in the map simulated environment. It holds information about its id, level of congestion and stops that are present on the street.
    Author:
    Michal Rein, Ondřej Motyčka
